    ## Our App's Dependencies

    As with many Flask apps, our application relies on a number of third party libraries to deliver this application. Some of the notable ones are:

    * [`flask`](//flask.pocoo.org/) : A microframework for Python
    * [`sqlalchemy`](//www.sqlalchemy.org/) : Object Relational Mapper that makes working in SQL easier.
    * [`authy`](https://github.com/authy/authy-python) : A high-level helper library for working with the Authy API

    Let's take a look at how our application is configured next.


