    ## Bootstrapping The Application

    We use this file to launch the Python process for our application. After pulling in external module dependencies, our bootstrap file has three jobs:


    1. Create and configure a Flask web application (our entire front end app will be a [Backbone](http://backbonejs.org) application served as static files from the `public` directory)
    1. Connect to our postgres database using SQLAlchemy
    1. Start our app on port 5000

